   09-06-2012 12:11 AM
   Our new school nurse kept my son in her office for an hour today and an
   hour yesterday. She wanted to send him home. He did have high numbers,
   but what the heck? Give him some insulin and get back to class! Am I
   wrong? He was in the low 300s and it was after lunch.
   [53]Report Inappropriate Content
